Function

in_dir <- "../data/figure_8d/"

make_count_table <- function(sample_name) {
  in_file <- paste(sample_name, "_LFC1_DESeq2_apeglm_res.csv", sep = "")

  df <- read_csv(paste(in_dir, sample_name, "/", in_file, sep = "")) |>
    drop_na(padj)

  filtered_df <- df |>
    filter(
      gene_symbol %in% c(
        "Lbr", "Tmpo", "Lmna"
      )
    )

  # Plot

  custom_col <- c(
    "Upregulated" = "#404788FF",
    "Unchanged" = "#999999",
    "Downregulated" = "#73D055FF"
  )

  plt_labelled <- ggplot(
    df,
    aes(
      x = log2FoldChange,
      y = -log10(padj),
      color = regulation_level
    )
  ) +
    geom_point(size = 1) +
    geom_vline(
      xintercept = c(-1, 1),
      color = "#252525",
      linetype = "dotted"
    ) +
    geom_hline(
      yintercept = 1.301,
      color = "#252525",
      linetype = "dotted"
    ) +
    geom_text_repel(
      data = filtered_df,
      aes(label = gene_symbol),
      size = 3,
      box.padding = 0.5,
      max.overlaps = 30,
      show.legend = FALSE
    ) +
    scale_color_manual(values = custom_col) +
    labs(
      x = expression("log"[2] * "(fold change)"),
      y = expression("-log"[10] * "(adjusted p-value)"),
      color = "Regulation \nlevel",
      title = sample_name
    ) +
    theme_bw()


  plt_labelled
}
